---
description: Apply the repository generic testing policy when editing tests.
globs:
  - "**/*.{test,spec}.{ts,tsx,js,jsx,mjs,cjs}"
  - "**/tests/**/*"
  - "**/Test*.php"
  - "**/*Test.php"
